Torture, From Persecution to Prison: The Health Consequences of&#13;
Detention for Asylum Seekers, June 2003, http://physiciansforhumanrights.org/library/documents/reports/report-perstoprison-2003.pdf&#13;
(accessed October 6, 2008).</p></div>
